nodes.text: Wuz was a male starfighter technician in the Rebel Alliance. He worked under Chief Nera Kase. Before the Battle of Yavin, Wuz worked on Jek Tono Porkins' X-wing. After Porkins' death in battle, Wuz left the Rebel war room in the Great Temple, due to guilt because Porkins' death appeared to be due to a mechanical error.
